  "description": "R36AH + Tube-UAC2 + AOA-2458-79AM + USB 2.0 cable + 12V DC adapter",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": null,
      "text": "WiFi CampPro 3 is an upgraded system designed for retrieving and extending Internet access in RV or yacht from remote Wi-Fi hotspots. If you need to boost a Wi-Fi signal to multiple devices at once, the WiFi CampPro 3 kit is the perfect choice!"
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "text": "Thanks to the upgraded version of the outdoor unit (Tube-UAC2), the WiFi CampPro 3 is now capable of connecting to dual-band hotspots 2.4 or 5 GHz, a/b/g/n/ac standards. With detailed printed instructions and easy to use QR code based setup, this kit can be quickly setup even by inexperienced users."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "text": "The kit includes:"
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "text": "1. Indoor unit (R36AH) with external antenna\n2. Outdoor unit (Tube-UAC2)\n3. Antenna for outdoor unit (AOA-2458-79AM)\n4. USB 2.0 cable (8 m length)\n5. Wall socket and car power adapters\n6. Installation accessories\n7. RJ45 Ethernet patch cord\n8. Installation guide"
    }
  ],
